{"tid":2358611,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"浸大學生記者採訪「和你Lunch」被捕　准保釋待 3 月再訊","createTime":"2021-01-08T09:08:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T11:06:10.000Z","uid":56115,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"23c041e6c6f69f280e5abef5db2c33e12e3ac40f","tid":2358611,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T09:08:37.000Z","msg":"去年 5 月 8 日，有市民在中環 ifc 商場「和你Lunch」，浸大學生記者鄧澤旻在採訪期間遭警方截查，期間涉不斷尖叫和反抗，被控以阻差辦公及拒捕兩罪。案件今（ 8 日）在東區裁判法院再度提訊，主任裁判官錢禮批准被告以原有保釋至 3 月 22 日再訊，以索取醫療報告。<br />\n<br />\n鄧*今日毋須答辯，辯方申請將案件押後至今年 3 月 22 日再訊獲批，以待索取醫療報告。據了解，辯方律師欲去信律政司商討，以其他方式處理本案。"},{"pid":"4c0827d31bbf49406dc90b48fc64052c1944e850","tid":2358611,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T09:08:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E6%B5%B8%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E6%8E%A1%E8%A8%AA-%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%A0lunch-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E5%87%86%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B%E5%BE%85-3-%E6%9C%88%E5%86%8D%E8%A8%8A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E6%25B5%25B8%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%258E%25A1%25E8%25A8%25AA-%25E5%2592%258C%25E4%25BD%25A0lunch-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E5%2587%2586%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%25E5%25BE%2585-3-%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25A8%258A%2F&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIdey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=4a672024\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E6%25B5%25B8%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%258E%25A1%25E8%25A8%25AA-%25E5%2592%258C%25E4%25BD%25A0lunch-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E5%2587%2586%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%25E5%25BE%2585-3-%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25A8%258A%2F&h=f21ff6db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E6%B5%B8%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E6%8E%A1%E8%A8%AA-%E